      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventive measure for this chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple, and the dash is free of pixel degradation. A true driver\u2019s car preserved in its peak performance envelope.",
