      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence that defines the term 'pristine.' This vehicle has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains flawless and free of any swirls or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather remains tight and supple, devoid of any creasing, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with the precision of a factory-fresh unit. We possess a comprehensive binder of every service record performed by certified technicians since day one. This is not merely a used car, but a collector-grade specimen for the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. No modifications, no track time, and an accident-free history make this the finest example currently on the market.",
