      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. This specific chassis is in concours condition, with preventative rod bearing service documented and a flawless carbon fiber roof maintaining structural rigidity. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. Every bushing, damper, and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) setting remains within factory tolerances, ensuring a surgical driving experience. Strictly maintained in a climate-controlled environment with zero track history.",
